        <item>
            <title>0.3.0  (2026-04-11)</title>
            <description>&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;Added &lt;code&gt;:MODEL&lt;/code&gt; keyword argument to &lt;a href=&quot;https://40ants.com/ai-agents/#x-2840ANTS-AI-AGENTS-2FAI-AGENT-3AAI-AGENT-20FUNCTION-29&quot; data-document=&quot;https://40ants.com/ai-agents/&quot; data-node=&quot;x-2840ANTS-AI-AGENTS-2FAI-AGENT-3AAI-AGENT-20FUNCTION-29&quot;&gt;&lt;code&gt;40ants-ai-agents/ai-agent:ai-agent&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt; function to allow per-call model override.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;Added &lt;code&gt;:ENDPOINT&lt;/code&gt; keyword argument to &lt;code&gt;40ants-ai-agents/ai-agent:ai-agent&lt;/code&gt; (&lt;a href=&quot;https://40ants.com/ai-agents/#x-2840ANTS-AI-AGENTS-2FAI-AGENT-3AAI-AGENT-20FUNCTION-29&quot; data-document=&quot;https://40ants.com/ai-agents/&quot; data-node=&quot;x-2840ANTS-AI-AGENTS-2FAI-AGENT-3AAI-AGENT-20FUNCTION-29&quot;&gt;&lt;code&gt;1&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;https://40ants.com/ai-agents/#x-2840ANTS-AI-AGENTS-2FAI-AGENT-3AAI-AGENT-20CLASS-29&quot; data-document=&quot;https://40ants.com/ai-agents/&quot; data-node=&quot;x-2840ANTS-AI-AGENTS-2FAI-AGENT-3AAI-AGENT-20CLASS-29&quot;&gt;&lt;code&gt;2&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt;).&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;Default endpoint is now derived from the model name: &lt;code&gt;deepseek-*&lt;/code&gt; uses &lt;code&gt;DeepSeek&lt;/code&gt;, &lt;code&gt;gpt-*/o1-*/o3-*/o4-*&lt;/code&gt; use &lt;code&gt;OpenAI&lt;/code&gt;, &lt;code&gt;claude-*&lt;/code&gt; uses &lt;code&gt;Anthropic&lt;/code&gt;, others fall back to &lt;code&gt;OpenAI&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;</description>
            <pubDate>Sat, 11 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
        </item>
